%% Forge Harness Engineering Data Flow
%% Shows how context flows through the system

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (PM)
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as forge-core
    participant T as Temporal
    participant AW as AI Worker
    participant CC as ContextCache
    participant LLM as LLM (qwen/claude)
    participant GH as GitHub

    U->>FE: Describe requirement
    FE->>API: POST /messages
    API->>T: AnalyzeRequirementWorkflow

    rect rgb(40, 40, 80)
        Note over AW,CC: Harness Layer
        T->>AW: analyze_requirement activity
        AW->>CC: get_or_build(project_id)
        CC-->>AW: MISS → fetch 4 APIs parallel
        CC-->>AW: SET → Redis cache (10min)
        AW->>LLM: AnalystAgent (no tools)
        LLM-->>AW: clarify question + options
    end

    AW-->>API: {status: "clarify", question, options}
    API-->>FE: SSE push
    FE-->>U: Show question + option buttons

    Note over U,FE: Multi-round Q&A (3-6 rounds)

    U->>FE: Confirm requirements
    FE->>API: POST /confirm
    API->>T: PlanOnlyWorkflow

    rect rgb(40, 40, 80)
        Note over AW,CC: Harness Layer + Tools
        T->>AW: plan_task activity
        AW->>CC: get_or_build → HIT (cached)
        AW->>LLM: PlannerAgent + tools
        LLM->>AW: tool_call: query_api_catalog("user")
        AW-->>LLM: [existing API endpoints]
        LLM->>AW: tool_call: query_module_graph("auth")
        AW-->>LLM: [module dependencies]
        LLM-->>AW: DAG plan + touched_files
    end

    AW-->>API: {tasks: [...], touched_files: {...}}
    API-->>FE: Plan review card + DAG viz
    U->>FE: Approve plan

    FE->>API: POST /approve-plan
    API->>T: TaskExecutionWorkflow

    rect rgb(40, 80, 40)
        Note over AW,LLM: Pipeline Execution
        T->>AW: generate_test_cases
        AW->>LLM: TestWriterAgent + tools
        T->>AW: generate_code (streaming)
        AW->>LLM: CoderAgent + all 5 tools
        AW-->>FE: SSE code tokens (real-time)
        T->>AW: review_code
        AW->>LLM: ReviewerAgent + tools
    end

    alt Review passed
        T->>AW: RunTests (K8s Job)
        T->>GH: PushToGitHub + CreatePR
        GH-->>API: PR #N created
        API-->>FE: Task COMPLETED + PR link
    else Review failed (max 3 attempts)
        T->>AW: re-generate with fix instructions
    end
